egin\": 1649, \"end\": 1661, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"score\": 0.9994762407729869, \"rank\": 0.0005240336564180829, \"text\": \"Amazon Prime\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This also comes with anAmazon Prime 30-day free trial.\", \"from\": 1680, \"to\": 1734, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Andy Jameson, BBC's main commentator for the coverage alongside Adrian Moorhouse, hailed the Frenchman after his history-making exploits in the capital.\", \"from\": 1736, \"to\": 1888, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1736, \"end\": 1748, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Jameson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Andy Jameson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Jameson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Jameson\"}, {\"begin\": 1750, \"end\": 1753, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.994849188393967, \"rank\": 0.005139943719031612, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}, {\"begin\": 1800, \"end\": 1816, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adrian_Moorhouse\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Adrian Moorhouse\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adrian_Moorhouse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adrian_Moorhouse\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Leon Marchand is an absolute sensation.\", \"from\": 1890, \"to\": 1930, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He's done the unthinkable, he's done the double.\", \"from\": 1931, \"to\": 1979, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He won the 200m butterfly in this session and also won the 200m breaststroke,\\\" Jameson said.\", \"from\": 1980, \"to\": 2072, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2059, \"end\": 2066, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fredric_Jameson\", \"score\": 0.9952299138834693, \"rank\": 0.00419601675417387, \"text\": \"Jameson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q4964182\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fredric_Jameson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fredric_Jameson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A double Olympic champion in one session.\", \"from\": 2074, \"to\": 2116, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I cannot believe it.\", \"from\": 2117, \"to\": 2137, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Not even Michael Phelps tried that - the audacity!\", \"from\": 2138, \"to\": 2188, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2147, \"end\": 2161, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2851171704864335e-50, \"text\": \"Michael Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"200 fly and 200 breaststroke - I cannot believe he even tried it, nevermind mind winning them both.\", \"from\": 2190, \"to\": 2290, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This guy is just off-the-scale brilliant.\", \"from\": 2291, \"to\": 2332, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The audacity to even try it.\", \"from\": 2334, \"to\": 2363, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Phelps did not try it, his coach, Phelps' old coach who coaches Marchand now, told Marchand to not even try it!\\\"\", \"from\": 2364, \"to\": 2476, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2364, \"end\": 2370, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"score\": 0.9999999878923519, \"rank\": 1.2106973478574671e-08, \"text\": \"Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelp